text.tspan: A patchbay-like pipeline editor for the rendering pipeline of OBS.
- Controls inputs and outputs of element
Effects can stay between a source and a scene
- Properties show in the node, up to a maximum size
- Limited to a single video and audio stream output
- Accept a single video and audio inputs
- Must come from a scene or a scene switcher
- Canvas resolution for input, custom video output resolution
- Limited to a single raw video stream input
- Single AV input and output optionally
Effects can also stay between scenes, scene switchers, and the encoders
- Limited to a single raw AV streams as input
The encoder must match the accepted
